{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775811359033,"sessionID":"ses_2896686e8ffeDN30MuvZxLFY1v","part":{"id":"prt_d76999aad001AON848JHckFvxN","messageID":"msg_d76998820001RR0Vbi8RScQGYo","sessionID":"ses_2896686e8ffeDN30MuvZxLFY1v","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_cf9fef9316e24469b314fedb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube pkg/apis","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project structure, focusing on:\n1. The overall project layout (list top-level directories and key files)\n2. The pkg/apis directory structure in detail\n3. Any existing CRD type definitions (look for types.go, register.go, doc.go files)\n4. Any existing shared types or constants\n5. The runtime/v1alpha1 API group specifically\n\nSearch in /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n\nReturn:\n- Full directory tree of pkg/apis/\n- Contents of any types.go, register.go, doc.go files found\n- Any existing constants or shared types\n- The SchemeGroupVersion definitions\n- Package naming conventions used","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2896653f1ffeCsj3ljVEvvJGlh (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is the complete exploration report for the AgentCube project.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Overall Project Layout (Top-Level)\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md\n├── changes/\n├── ci-cd/\n├── cli-toolkit/\n├── code-execution/\n├── coverage.out\n├── deployment/\n├── go.mod\n├── go.sum\n├── idle-cleanup/\n├── integrations/\n├── pkg/\n├── project.md\n├── python-sdk/\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n├── session-routing/\n├── session-store/\n├── test_spec.md\n└── testing/\n```\n\nThe `pkg/` directory contains only `apis/` at this time:\n\n```\npkg/\n└── apis/\n    └── runtime/\n        └── v1alpha1/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Full Directory Tree of `pkg/apis/`\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── agent_type.go                    # AgentRuntime CRD type definitions\n        ├── agent_type_test.go               # Tests for AgentRuntime types\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go         # CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go    # Tests for CodeInterpreter types\n        ├── doc.go                           # Go doc + k8s codegen markers\n        ├── groupversion_info.go             # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n        ├── groupversion_info_test.go        # Tests for scheme registration\n        ├── register.go                      # Kind constants, SchemeGroupVersion alias, Resource() helper\n        ├── register_test.go                 # Tests for register.go constants/helpers\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go         # Auto-generated DeepCopy methods\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. CRD Type Definitions\n\n### doc.go\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n### register.go\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\nvar (\n\tCodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n\tCodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n\tCodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n\tCodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n)\n\nvar (\n\tAgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n\tAgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n\tAgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n\treturn GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n### groupversion_info.go\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\t\"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n)\n\nvar (\n\tGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n\n\tSchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n\n\tAddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Existing CRD Types\n\n### AgentRuntime (in `agent_type.go`)\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n\n| Type | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `AgentRuntime` | CRD root type (namespaced, with subresource:status) |\n| `AgentRuntimeSpec` | Spec with `Ports`, `Template` (*SandboxTemplate), `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration` |\n| `SandboxTemplate` | Pod template with `Labels`, `Annotations`, `Spec` (corev1.PodSpec) |\n| `AgentRuntimeStatus` | Status with `Conditions` ([]metav1.Condition) |\n| `AgentRuntimeList` | List type |\n\nKey kubebuilder markers:\n- `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`\n- `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n- `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n\n### CodeInterpreter (in `codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n\n| Type | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `CodeInterpreter` | CRD root type (namespaced, with subresource:status) |\n| `CodeInterpreterSpec` | Spec with `Ports`, `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`, `WarmPoolSize`, `AuthMode` |\n| `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` | Sandbox template with `Labels`, `Annotations`, `RuntimeClassName`, `Image`, `ImagePullPolicy`, `ImagePullSecrets`, `Environment`, `Command`, `Args`, `Resources` |\n| `CodeInterpreterStatus` | Status with `Conditions` and `Ready` (bool) |\n| `CodeInterpreterList` | List type |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Existing Shared Types and Constants\n\n### String-based type aliases and constants (in `codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n\tProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n\tProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n\tAuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n\tAuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n### Shared helper type: `TargetPort` (in `codeinterpreter_types.go`, reused by `agent_type.go`)\n\n```go\ntype TargetPort struct {\n\tPathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n\tName       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n\tPort       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n\tProtocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\nThis type is defined in `codeinterpreter_types.go` and referenced by `AgentRuntimeSpec.Ports` in `agent_type.go`.\n\n---\n\n## 6. SchemeGroupVersion Definitions\n\nDefined in `groupversion_info.go`:\n```go\nGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n```\n\nAliased in `register.go`:\n```go\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n```\n\nThe `SchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` are also defined in `groupversion_info.go` using `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme`. Each CRD type registers itself via `init()`:\n```go\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})\n}\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. Package Naming Conventions\n\n| Convention | Example |\n|------------|---------|\n| Go module | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| API group domain | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| API version package | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` (all lowercase version)